data.description: MOTIVATED SELLER!! Welcome to this charming open concept residence located in the beautiful city of Fort Worth, Texas. This home offers 4 bedrooms, 2 bath with 1,627 sq.ft of living space that boasts a warm and inviting atmosphere, perfect for creating lasting memories with your loved ones. You'll have easy access to a variety of shopping, dining and entertainment options. Plus, with convenient access to major highways. Just a few minutes from Eagle Mountain Lake.
